hot er gefunen a yidn a blekher dortn, a, a

00:05:21.970 --> 00:05:24.833
vos er hot genumen im lernen.

00:05:25.952 --> 00:05:27.093
dem JOSEF.

00:05:27.775 --> 00:05:31.228
er hot bay dem yidn, di f- di froy hot mir yetst dertseylt

00:05:34.575 --> 00:05:35.986
ikh ken zi vayzn do

00:05:35.841 --> 00:05:38.113
no- nokh nisht. m'vet shpeter vayzn.

00:05:36.263 --> 00:05:36.982
ne-

00:05:40.549 --> 00:05:42.348
der yid, meyn ikh

00:05:46.793 --> 00:05:48.305
hot getun guts far im.

