un iz gevorn a, a mekhanik. er hot gelernt in shule oykhet dortn.

00:06:10.671 --> 00:06:12.183
ven er hot mir gefunen

00:06:12.257 --> 00:06:15.255
hot er gehat a, a yidish, a bisl yidish harts

00:06:15.683 --> 00:06:16.875
fun yenem yidn.

00:06:17.978 --> 00:06:20.649
far dem zogt tsu mir yetst di goye

00:06:20.649 --> 00:06:23.509
er zogt "er ⟨iz di⟩ gold, nisht ikh." far vos?

00:06:23.509 --> 00:06:25.695
vayl ikh hob ir gebrakht a CADEAU

00:06:25.695 --> 00:06:27.809
a k- a goldene keyt mit a tseylem.

00:06:28.896 --> 00:06:32.838
un nokh dos farshidene zakhn, hob ikh ir gegebn, zogt zi mir "se kumt mir nisht."

00:06:33.317 --> 00:06:35.791
va- vayl dos hot fardint mayn man.

00:06:37.536 --> 00:06:38.508
erlekh.

00:06:40.708 --> 00:06:42.389
iz far dem hot er mir geholfn.

00:06:44.573 --> 00:06:45.630
meyn ikh.

00:06:46.598 --> 00:06:48.600
es iz, logish iz dos azoy.

00:06:49.956 --> 00:06:56.295
ven ikh hob gehat gan beheymes pashen zayne, un zayn bruder's oykhet hot er mir gegebn.

00:06:56.790 --> 00:06:58.280
iz fleg ikh shoyn geyt gut

00:06:58.280 --> 00:07:01.510
flegn durkhgeyn ukrainer, UNK zayn tsvishn beheymes

00:07:01.510 --> 00:07:02.750
a shtekn hob ikh gehat

00:07:02.848 --> 00:07:08.360
az ikh hob gezen geyn politsey tsi ver, fleg ikh gebn a klap UNK flegn zey loyfn, fleg ikh ⟨oykh⟩ loyfn.

00:07:08.890 --> 00:07:11.702
iz heyst dos az ikh antloyf nisht.

00:07:15.133 --> 00:07:17.337
ikh kum in feld arayn mit di beheymes

00:07:18.171 --> 00:07:20.848
un di ku vos ikh hob geshlofn mit ir

00:07:20.871 --> 00:07:22.738
hot zi bay im nisht gevolt pashen

00:07:24.128 --> 00:07:24.965
friert.

00:07:24.972 --> 00:07:27.246
er fleg tsubindn dem kop tsu di fis

00:07:27.246 --> 00:07:29.859
zol nisht kenen antloyfn, un zi fleg esn azoy.

00:07:30.523 --> 00:07:32.055
un zi fleg kumen moger.

00:07:32.055 --> 00:07:33.672
er hot gehat problemen mit ir.

00:07:34.050 --> 00:07:36.153
ven ikh bin gekumen pashen ir

00:07:38.607 --> 00:07:40.139
zi iz geven gevoynt mit mir

00:07:40.139 --> 00:07:42.499
fleg ikh nisht tsubindn dem kop tsu di fis

00:07:42.808 --> 00:07:44.138
un fleg oplozn.

00:07:44.138 --> 00:07:45.480
dos iz geven geferlekh

00:07:45.480 --> 00:07:47.240
nor ikh hob gevolt zi zol onnemen

00:07:48.546 --> 00:07:50.480
⟨vi⟩ azoy flegn zey brengen tsurik

00:07:51.111 --> 00:07:55.762
ven ikh, far vos hot zi geesn dos gro- dos shtroy unter zikh

00:07:56.983 --> 00:07:58.411
yetst farshtey ikh

00:07:58.722 --> 00:08:01.534
kh'hob zikh PIPI gemakht dortn, un dos iz gezaltsn.

00:08:01.725 --> 00:08:03.221
fleg zi oyfesn di shtroy.

00:08:04.628 --> 00:08:07.457
ven ikh fleg zi oplozn, ikh hob zi gevolt nemen tsurik

00:08:07.598 --> 00:08:09.819
iz geven vayt. zi fleg zikh pashen aleyn.

00:08:09.893 --> 00:08:11.591
geven a yidishe kluge ku.

00:08:12.981 --> 00:08:14.277
on andere ki

00:08:14.277 --> 00:08:16.437
un, aleyn hot zi gehat mel

00:08:16.437 --> 00:08:17.784
un di beste grozn

00:08:18.297 --> 00:08:22.997
zolst mir moykhl zayn, fleg ikh zikh avekshteln PIPI makhn, un fleg shrayen

00:08:22.997 --> 00:08:25.257
 fleg zi oys⟨UNK⟩ dem tsung

00:08:25.257 --> 00:08:27.555
 un fleg kumen tsu mir.

00:08:27.713 --> 00:08:31.858
hobn di shk- di tshekhn di shkotsim gezogt az ikh bin a kishef makher.

00:08:32.421 --> 00:08:34.592
ikh hob shoyn geredt tshekhish a bisl.

