zey hobn gemeynt ikh bin a polyak. polyakn UNK enlekh.

00:08:38.125 --> 00:08:41.494
flegn zey mir zogn, s'flegn a mol aroysgeyn yidn funem vald

00:08:42.107 --> 00:08:43.805
m'hot gezen, farvaksene

