ikh hob gekukt ven ikh UNK kh'hob gebrakht di beheyme

00:09:02.323 --> 00:09:04.294
geven azoy breyt ongepashet

00:09:04.294 --> 00:09:07.953
fleg zi shteyn un kukn un e- zikh aleyn nisht gleybn.

00:09:10.356 --> 00:09:12.290
bin ikh shoyn a nits man geven.

