bin ikh shoyn geven a bisl zikher bay zikh az m'vet mir nisht oysgebn.

00:09:18.017 --> 00:09:19.833
varshayndlekh hot er geredt mit ir.

00:09:20.650 --> 00:09:23.107
fun vanet kumen azoyne nutsn veys ikh nisht.

00:09:28.716 --> 00:09:29.942
normal

00:09:33.002 --> 00:09:34.447
keyn eyn filosof

00:09:35.550 --> 00:09:36.961
keyn eyn shrayber

00:09:38.503 --> 00:09:40.134
⟨vet nisht tsunoyfshteln⟩

00:09:43.262 --> 00:09:45.416
punkt azoy vos der kumt

