ikh hob getun azoyne arbetn

00:10:54.525 --> 00:10:58.872
az er hot nisht gekent forsht- e- er iz geven zikher az ikh bin fun a dorf.

00:10:59.470 --> 00:11:01.033
a dorf man bin ikh gevorn.

00:11:03.503 --> 00:11:06.231
un dos kind iz geboyrn gevorn bay im

00:11:06.287 --> 00:11:09.521
in AUGUST, un ikh bin geven, dos iz zeks monatn geven.

00:11:10.017 --> 00:11:11.074
eyn mol

00:11:11.755 --> 00:11:12.964
kumen daytshn

00:11:13.392 --> 00:11:14.533
mit ukrayner

00:11:16.210 --> 00:11:18.651
un fregn, un ikh ze zey geyen

00:11:18.960 --> 00:11:20.557
un ikh bin geven in shtal

00:11:21.745 --> 00:11:24.152
trakht i- zey geyen in dem rikhtung.

00:11:24.850 --> 00:11:26.375
oyb m'vet im tsukvetshn

00:11:26.375 --> 00:11:28.835
