00:12:04.084 --> 00:12:07.149
az yetst redt ikh mit aza aktsent tshekhish.

00:12:12.083 --> 00:12:14.119
ikh meyn mentshn in

00:12:14.783 --> 00:12:16.025
in tsores

00:12:16.420 --> 00:12:17.865
hobn besere kep.

00:12:19.508 --> 00:12:20.649
azoy meyn ikh.

00:12:21.600 --> 00:12:24.395
a frayer mentsh ken nisht azoy shnel khapn

