ikh her dortn UNK, leyg ikh zikh avek ⟨hintern⟩ koymen

00:12:45.411 --> 00:12:47.615
un der daytsh heybt zikh oyf oyvn

00:12:48.178 --> 00:12:49.533
oyfn leyter

00:12:49.533 --> 00:12:53.063
un der JOSEF iz zikher ikh bin dortn nishto

00:12:53.063 --> 00:12:54.603
vayl er veys ikh bin dortn.

00:12:56.059 --> 00:12:58.112
un kuk. ikh ze dem shotn fun im.

00:12:59.417 --> 00:13:01.498
v- ⟨vayl⟩ di shayn funem fentster

00:13:01.498 --> 00:13:02.797
ze ikh azoy di shotn

