00:23:44.633 --> 00:23:48.187
in di bremes, in di oyern. umedum iz geven layz.

00:23:48.193 --> 00:23:50.713
un s'iz geven azoyne layz, mit eyer

00:23:50.713 --> 00:23:51.396
az

00:23:51.396 --> 00:23:53.418
az m'hot zey nisht gekent aroysnemen.

00:23:53.526 --> 00:23:55.033
ikh bin farlayzikt bin ikh geven.

00:23:55.033 --> 00:23:56.557
kh'hob gehat a pelts

00:23:56.952 --> 00:23:59.539
a pelts a, aza futer.

00:23:59.539 --> 00:24:00.894
vu hob ikh im genumen?

00:24:01.525 --> 00:24:03.291
ikh hob

00:24:03.465 --> 00:24:06.584
ven ikh bin aroys funem vald, oykh funem himl gefaln

00:24:06.584 --> 00:24:07.881
iz geven hey

00:24:08.713 --> 00:24:10.597
iz, iz geven kalt

00:24:10.620 --> 00:24:14.411
hob ikh, hob ikh, a- di hey shteyt azoy

00:24:14.586 --> 00:24:15.812
tsunoyfgeleygt

00:24:16.223 --> 00:24:17.719
bin ikh arayn oyvn

00:24:17.843 --> 00:24:19.687
un ikh hob arayngeshtupt di fis

00:24:19.687 --> 00:24:21.482
un in hey iz geven varemer.

00:24:22.450 --> 00:24:25.346
iz in kalt iz geven, hob ikh nisht gehat vos ontsutun.

00:24:28.525 --> 00:24:31.252
mit a mol gey- geyt a

00:24:31.393 --> 00:24:32.231
a

00:24:32.558 --> 00:24:35.837
a froy mit a, a shikse mit a sheygets

00:24:35.837 --> 00:24:37.665
un me leygt avek dem pelts

00:24:37.840 --> 00:24:40.078
bay dem hey, un me zetst zikh avek dortn.

00:24:40.624 --> 00:24:44.806
ikh i- ikh hob zikh gegebn azoy a rir, iz dos hey aropgefaln oyf zey

00:24:44.806 --> 00:24:47.006
iz zey hobn ongehoybn tsu loyfn

00:24:47.006 --> 00:24:50.036
shreklekh. m'hot zikh dershrokn. ikh hob gekhapt dem pelts

00:24:50.063 --> 00:24:51.064
un bin avek.

00:24:52.977 --> 00:24:54.675
hob ikh bakumen dem pelts

00:24:55.103 --> 00:25:00.041
un der pelts hot zikh ongefilt mit layz, zol got ophitn.

00:25:00.418 --> 00:25:04.090
ikh fleg im aroysshteln oyfn fro- oyfn, in droysn

00:25:05.380 --> 00:25:08.715
un s'iz geven kalt, hob ikh gemeynt s'vet farfroyrn vern di layz.

00:25:09.953 --> 00:25:12.022
 ⟨vel ikh⟩ dokh poter vern.

00:25:13.041 --> 00:25:14.638
ikh fleg azoy oysshitn

00:25:14.880 --> 00:25:16.455
un s'iz geven lekhlekh

00:25:16.455 --> 00:25:17.439
in shney

00:25:17.749 --> 00:25:19.025
fun dem pelts.

00:25:19.757 --> 00:25:23.936
un ikh fleg im ontun, hob ikh geven fartik. UNK poter gevorn. a nekhtiker tog.

00:25:24.111 --> 00:25:26.062
azoy az s'iz varem gevorn tsurik

00:25:26.068 --> 00:25:28.475
kh'hob zikh tsugevoynt. zey flegn mir nisht baysn.

00:25:29.072 --> 00:25:30.095
gornisht.

00:25:30.895 --> 00:25:31.867
nor

00:25:32.835 --> 00:25:35.211
nor ven di rusn hobn derzen mir

00:25:35.211 --> 00:25:37.065
mit, mit di layz mit alemen

00:25:37.273 --> 00:25:40.946
un oyf mayn mazl hot zikh geyavet a, a yid a mayor.

00:25:41.222 --> 00:25:42.633
er hot mir derzen

00:25:43.399 --> 00:25:45.637
hot er mir genumen in, in Rovne

00:25:47.044 --> 00:25:49.265
in a militer shpitol

00:25:49.778 --> 00:25:51.403
un er hot gezogt eyne

00:25:51.403 --> 00:25:53.416
LUPINA MARIA FEDOROVNA

00:25:53.305 --> 00:25:54.463
vos meynt dos?

00:25:54.148 --> 00:25:54.769
z-

00:25:54.769 --> 00:25:57.113
zi hot geheysn di familye LUPINA

00:25:57.253 --> 00:26:00.537
MARIA, nokhn foter FEDOROVNA. rusish geyt dos azoy.

00:26:02.890 --> 00:26:04.861
un hot ir gezogt

00:26:04.861 --> 00:26:07.237
er zol zen mir tsubrengen

00:26:07.767 --> 00:26:09.347
in a mentshlekhn oyfn.

00:26:09.842 --> 00:26:11.591
ikh bin geven a monat tsayt

00:26:11.648 --> 00:26:12.941
in dem shpitol.

00:26:13.437 --> 00:26:14.696
zey flegn mir

00:26:15.141 --> 00:26:16.451
⟨vi⟩ azoy a muter

00:26:17.385 --> 00:26:22.070
tsi zi hot gehat a bafel, a bafel iz a bafel, nor mentshlekh iz mentshlekh.

00:26:22.245 --> 00:26:23.876
zi hot mir azoy bahandlt

00:26:24.338 --> 00:26:27.085
az in a khoydesh bin ikh gevorn nisht keyn mentsh

00:26:27.085 --> 00:26:28.230
bin gevorn a

00:26:28.540 --> 00:26:30.171
a gvaldiker mentsh.

00:26:30.177 --> 00:26:31.892
esn un trinken

00:26:32.016 --> 00:26:36.178
un aroysgenumen, kh'hob do lekhlekh un do lekhlekh, iz nor d-

00:26:37.213 --> 00:26:40.194
f- f- fun, fun di layz, fun alemen

00:26:40.217 --> 00:26:42.135
un keyn eyn tog

00:26:42.327 --> 00:26:43.839
bin ikh krank nisht geven.

00:26:44.065 --> 00:26:46.253
afile fun di noz hot nisht gerunen.

00:26:46.360 --> 00:26:49.054
ikh bin geven a shtik beton.

00:26:50.663 --> 00:26:53.782
vi azoy dos kumt for veys ikh nisht. dos vil zogn azoy.

00:26:53.782 --> 00:26:57.120
az kinder vos zey geyen in varem un kalt

00:26:57.598 --> 00:27:01.653
i- iz, iz zey baytn di temperaturn, denstmol vern zey krank.

00:27:01.653 --> 00:27:03.819
a mentsh vos iz imer in di kalt

00:27:03.960 --> 00:27:05.321
un shmuts

00:27:05.462 --> 00:27:07.295
az se ⟨geloynt⟩ im farshtendlekh

00:27:07.352 --> 00:27:08.443
iz er shtark.

00:27:10.288 --> 00:27:13.238
nokh dem ven du bist dikh, tsurikgekumen tsu zikh

00:27:10.845 --> 00:27:11.969
un no-

00:27:13.238 --> 00:27:16.068
ven bist shoyn beser gevorn

00:27:15.520 --> 00:27:20.745
ikh bin beser gevorn, bin ikh gan, hot men mir ongetun in militer forme.

00:27:20.818 --> 00:27:22.989
m'hot ⟨mir⟩ spetsyel far mir oyfgeneyt.

00:27:23.063 --> 00:27:25.149
vi alt bistu geven in di tsayt?

00:27:25.594 --> 00:27:28.746
dos iz azoy geven. dos iz geven fir un fertsik.

00:27:28.746 --> 00:27:32.068
meyn ikh bin geven fuftsn un zekhtsn yor.

00:27:32.563 --> 00:27:33.620
bin a yingl.

00:27:34.403 --> 00:27:35.631
bin ikh avek m-

00:27:35.631 --> 00:27:37.315
mi- mit dem

00:27:38.323 --> 00:27:39.690
mit di militer

00:27:39.690 --> 00:27:41.973
denstmol hot zikh gerukt di front shoyn vayter

00:27:42.756 --> 00:27:45.028
s- s'ershte bin ikh aroyfgeforn

00:27:45.068 --> 00:27:46.918
zen in Lutsk tsi emetser iz do.

00:27:49.692 --> 00:27:51.266
ikh hob keynem nisht gefunen

00:27:51.266 --> 00:27:53.465
iz dos geven nisht, nisht vayt

00:27:53.556 --> 00:27:55.963
bin ikh tsurikgekumen, un mit di militer

00:27:56.188 --> 00:27:58.291
bin ikh gan dem gantsn front

00:27:58.703 --> 00:28:00.013
biz Berlin.

00:28:01.217 --> 00:28:02.645
bin geven in Poyln

00:28:03.006 --> 00:28:04.535
geven in DEUTSCHLAND

00:28:05.453 --> 00:28:06.083
un

00:28:06.083 --> 00:28:08.215
bizn zeks un fertsikstn yor

00:28:08.625 --> 00:28:10.121
bin ikh geven in DEUTSCHLAND.

00:28:10.212 --> 00:28:14.436
zog mir, farn zeks un fertsikstn yor, ven du bist geven mitn militer

00:28:13.215 --> 00:28:14.339
yo

00:28:14.436 --> 00:28:19.267
hostu bafrayt a lager, epes geven in lager az du host gezen epes?

00:28:18.936 --> 00:28:22.254
i- ikh hob gezen fun, fun Tshenstokhov.

00:28:23.121 --> 00:28:24.459
ikh hob gezen

00:28:24.459 --> 00:28:26.979
yidn fun, fun Belgye

00:28:26.985 --> 00:28:28.447
fun Frankraykh

00:28:28.909 --> 00:28:32.804
, fun di amerikaner

00:28:32.804 --> 00:28:34.424
gefangene hobn beser gehat.

00:28:34.424 --> 00:28:36.598
zey hobn gehat funem roytn KREUTZ

00:28:36.756 --> 00:28:39.048
hobn zey gehat shokolad

00:28:39.048 --> 00:28:40.431
farshidene zakhn.

00:28:40.431 --> 00:28:42.926
di rusishe gefangene hobn gornisht gehat.

00:28:43.050 --> 00:28:46.621
zey zenen geven oyf groyse tsores, un di yidn nishto vos tsu redn geven.

00:28:46.847 --> 00:28:48.514
s'iz ge- s'iz gegan

00:28:48.514 --> 00:28:51.594
re- kolones gantse, farshidene

00:28:51.594 --> 00:28:53.321
mit fla- mit fanen

00:28:53.682 --> 00:28:57.287
fun Belgye, fun dortn, fun dortn, fun dortn

00:28:58.238 --> 00:29:00.926
un di yidn

00:29:00.926 --> 00:29:02.281
flegn mir zeyer helfn.

00:29:02.727 --> 00:29:07.159
s'iz geven a sakh yidishe ofitsern. me fleg avekshteln a kikh

00:29:07.333 --> 00:29:08.694
un esn gebn

00:29:09.088 --> 00:29:11.208
un m'hot zeyer geholfn. ikh ken dos zogn

00:29:11.333 --> 00:29:14.432
shlekhts oyf, oyf Rusland

00:29:14.607 --> 00:29:16.052
a dank Rusland

00:29:16.227 --> 00:29:18.434
zenen a sakh mentshn geratevet gevorn

00:29:18.434 --> 00:29:20.287
vayl di amerikaner zenen gekumen shpeter.

00:29:20.614 --> 00:29:22.717
di hoyptzakh hobn gemakht di rusn.

00:29:23.348 --> 00:29:25.451
me fleg kushn di shtivl poshet.

00:29:26.115 --> 00:29:27.476
me fleg veynen.

00:29:30.773 --> 00:29:33.587
s'iz nisht tsu bashraybn normal di situatsye.

00:29:33.587 --> 00:29:35.165
ikh hob gornisht genumen

00:29:35.165 --> 00:29:39.185
vayl m'hot erloybt, yeder rus hot gekent nemen tsen kilo

00:29:39.185 --> 00:29:42.115
vos er hot gevolt shikn nokh Rusland. ikh hob nisht gehat vemen tsu shikn.

00:29:42.115 --> 00:29:44.010
ikh hob gefunen azoyne zakhn.

00:29:44.010 --> 00:29:45.810
ikh bin geven in DRESDEN GALEREYA

00:29:45.810 --> 00:29:47.380
iz geven azoyne bilder

00:29:47.380 --> 00:29:49.214
az m'hot gekent ⟨a milyoner⟩ vern

00:29:49.214 --> 00:29:51.160
ikh fleg mitn fus klapn.

00:29:52.103 --> 00:29:53.433
vart, halt a minut.
